{"tid":1426042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"義士人血饅頭好味嗎?","createTime":"2019-08-07T00:24:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T04:03:13.000Z","uid":285664,"like":18,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"10ac7af53b3fb4c02c947638623806d3d4186144","tid":1426042,"uid":285664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:24:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔分化、唔割蓆，原則上係啱嘅。但如果你覺得犧牲前途同生命嘅義士要爭取嘅，只係單單成立一個無法解決制度問題嘅獨立調查委員會的話<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你就係食義士人血饅頭嘅仆街!!!!割你老母蓆係應份嘅!!!</span><br />\n<br />\n點玩、點發夢都得，但唔堅持以下兩點，你就係滿口鮮血嘅甲級戰犯!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">1. 爭取五大訴求到底，包括雙普選，缺一不可</span><br />\n(淨係叫獨立調查委員會，就係解散軍，現時左膠同建制大力吹奏)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">2. 無大台，無領袖，不代表談判，直到五大訴求全部達成</span><br />\n(無人可以代表義士!! 參加左膠活動，一定要格外留神而且時刻警剔佢哋言論，何式凝就是最佳例子。) </span>"},{"pid":"576bc67eda48a1f74e0f62aaa923c149b4299292","tid":1426042,"uid":285664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:25:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54779a254525ccd44ccb331d50c1e76f47b8d7fe","tid":1426042,"uid":285664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:25:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0873b1ba732db63be7af3a84bda740549e9a55f1","tid":1426042,"uid":285664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:25:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"826a68e9d244f53be23adce1442ffa3a0f08f0cb","tid":1426042,"uid":285664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:25:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9229ccffe7cbd5d372726cc2ea65c1aa02a118f8","tid":1426042,"uid":285664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:25:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dfcabb05cc2e0983951ea822201ab5692005c415","tid":1426042,"uid":285664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:26:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73502bb3d7afaa6dc543b594c842699667bbaa40","tid":1426042,"uid":285664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim